<title>GERMANY: Goldschmidt H1 1996 pre-tax profit rises.</title>
<headline>Goldschmidt H1 1996 pre-tax profit rises.</headline>
<dateline>ESSEN, Germany 1996-08-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Six months to end June</p>
<p>(in millions of marks unless stated)</p>
<p>    Group pre-tax profit		     26.3    vs 20.3</p>
<p>    Group sales				  636     vs 618.1</p>
<p>Of which</p>
<p>     Domestic sales			    255.9   vs 267.9</p>
<p>     Foreign sales			     380.1   vs 350.2</p>
<p>    Investments				  56.2    vs 59.2</p>
<p>    Workforce at end June		    5,976   vs 5,847</p>
<p>    Parent pre-tax profit		    25.2    vs 21.7</p>
<p>    Parent sales				 272.9   vs 290.1</p>
<p>Of which</p>
<p>     Domestic sales			    141.1   vs 149.9</p>
<p>     Foreign sales			     131.8   vs 140.2</p>
<p>    Parent investments			 27	vs 36.1</p>
<p>    Parent workforce at end June	   1,686  vs 1,765</p>
<p>NOTE - Full name of the German chemicals company is Th. Goldschmidt AG.</p>
<p>--Frankfurt Newsroom, +49 69 756525</p>
</text>
